{"tid":1697921,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"北川景子剪短招牌長髮","createTime":"2019-11-07T07:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T08:02:00.000Z","uid":44730,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b655d8f842d8a905bfcefb2e387e50d0bcc773ca","tid":1697921,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"33歲北川景子與DAIGO結婚三年，今年8月一度傳出二人婚變消息，傳聞鬧得熱烘烘之時，DAIGO趁妻子牛一當日留言放閃，並貼上一束紅玫瑰的照片，實行以行動闢謠。<br />\n<br />\n景子一向是圈中美女，一把招牌長髮更令人印象深刻。今日宣佈為女作家島本理生作品《初戀》拍攝真人電影版，剪短髮飾演臨床心理學家真壁由紀，故事描述志願成為主播的女大學生聖山環菜，在接受完主播面試完後，她拿着早已準備好的菜刀，順路到父親工作的藝術學校，刺殺了身為知名畫家的父親。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191107/large/1573102271_6440.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191107%2Flarge%2F1573102271_6440.jpg&h=b435e2ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac5af24875be2fd88c822a4d8d734ba0cdf71418","tid":1697921,"uid":44730,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:14:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UHRh00983l8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUHRh00983l8&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=26f11399\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UHRh00983l8</a><br />\n<br />\n諗起零秒出手 原來岩岩過左十年  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8c272f7d195463f6a7b110035fa2a18058d0930","tid":1697921,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:15:12.000Z","msg":"臨床心理學家真壁由紀受委託，計劃將聖山環菜的故事撰寫成書，與聖山環菜接觸後，由紀卻發現，在環菜身上缺失了關鍵記憶，若找到記憶中那段初戀，或可解開她的殺父謎團。《初戀》原著小說已賣出12萬本，並成為去年直木賞得獎作品。"},{"pid":"f51b9c318dc239620fb7da7464c3befa30c7e6b4","tid":1697921,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:15:26.000Z","msg":"景子將長髮剪短30cm，望忠於今次角色，為觀眾帶來新鮮感，電影由堤幸彦執導，已在10月開鏡，預計下月中煞科，安排2021年上映。"},{"pid":"aa8ae4b5ea5f9fa1646d3b1b701bbda0f0509565","tid":1697921,"uid":265179,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:16:03.000Z","msg":"短髮女好靚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e928a4adb2613ce4eb08a01867d5eb2a3722a0c1","tid":1697921,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:23:16.000Z","msg":"又幾襯"},{"pid":"75a04014f7deab969017ba40b0e6a45af6e14f22","tid":1697921,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:24:37.000Z","msg":"一樣好靚..."},{"pid":"85b132d994a73de52a3ab39dd536401f45ca2859","tid":1697921,"uid":190829,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa8ae4b5ea5f9fa1646d3b1b701bbda0f0509565","tid":1697921,"uid":265179,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:16:03.000Z","msg":"短髮女好靚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:25:27.000Z","msg":"本田翼BB"},{"pid":"b0db52fd47092f3cad315b6024af5647d2957b80","tid":1697921,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:27:22.000Z","msg":"原來先33<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e723bcb57cb0a4ba2cfe31ad75e981dfa709fcc","tid":1697921,"uid":188311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:29:31.000Z","msg":"佢講&quot;go&quot;個樣好搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8c40f2f66d74fb5a53bbae1e7070fa6dcdc804","tid":1697921,"uid":35451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:30:24.000Z","msg":"都唔差<br />\n不過右面真係幾屈機"},{"pid":"31491570857c51e94cb80c31567266337dd71708","tid":1697921,"uid":152123,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b655d8f842d8a905bfcefb2e387e50d0bcc773ca","tid":1697921,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco